# This repo holds docs/scripts/releases only — the AOSP/LineageOS source tree
# lives on this same drive (android/lineage, symlinked from ~/android/lineage)
# for disk-space reasons, but must never be tracked here. It contains, among
# other things, NeonOS's private signing keys
# (android/lineage/vendor/lineage-priv/keys/) — these must never be committed
# or pushed anywhere, per explicit Product Owner instruction (2026-07-11).
android/

# Build logs and the build-host swapfile — local machine state, not project docs.
*.log
swapfile

# Claude Code's own local tool config/settings — machine-local, not project source,
# and not meant to be public on the GitHub repo.
.claude/

# Internal AI-collaboration process docs (agent instructions, session-by-session build
# narration, product roadmap) -- kept local-only per explicit Product Owner instruction
# (2026-07-13): the public repo's surface is code, scripts, docs/BUILDING.md, docs/OTA.md,
# and the OTA manifests only.
CLAUDE.md
DEVELOPMENT_PLAN.md
NEON_PROJECT.md
